title: HOUR 3- Eli Gold Oct 16, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Eli Gold Oct 16, 2020
description:
Eli Gold tells Dan that he cant imagine what Nick Saban would be like if he had to stay home during an Alabama game even if Nick does have the Covid19. Eli says that he himself has been broadcasting Alabama games for 32 years and he would go crazy if he ever had to miss an Alabama game.
